This plugin provides a customizable Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA) system for OPNsense,
offering Time-based One-Time Password (TOTP) support compatible with apps such as Google Authenticator.

Key Features:
- Enforces a second authentication factor during login.
- QR code generation and TOTP setup from the OPNsense GUI.
- Secure secret storage and per-user management.
- Integrates with OPNsense login flow via patching.
- Backed by the robust `pyotp` library.

